      <title>给爱看书的人，推荐两款豆瓣读书插件</title>
      <link>https://colarxu.github.io/posts/2024/%E7%BB%99%E7%88%B1%E7%9C%8B%E4%B9%A6%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E4%B8%A4%E6%AC%BE%E8%B1%86%E7%93%A3%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</link>
